longBusinessSummary: 808 Renewable Energy Corporation, through its subsidiaries, designs, develops, manufactures, distributes, and markets general aviation and electric vehicles in the United States. It offers AR-1 gyrocopter and electric reverse-trike vehicles under the Dagger, Arrow, and Orca names through distributors and dealers. The company was formerly known as Tri-Energy Corporation and changed its name to 808 Renewable Energy Corporation in August 2021. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Bradenton, Florida.
